{"tid":1333101,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 觀塘已經岀現多支(監控)智慧燈柱","createTime":"2019-07-19T14:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:30:11.000Z","uid":283125,"like":104,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe4a74197c392ab70fc1bdebbef15cff5b008fe","tid":1333101,"uid":283125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"我係觀塘人，由細到大都係觀塘長大。<br />\n<br />\n心諗做乜撚嘢搞鳩我呢D觀塘人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一直都係齋睇連登，唔會留言，但係呢件事覺得事態嚴重所以要post出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最近發現物華街 ，觀月樺峯等一帶岀現所謂智慧燈柱。單單係一條物華街已經有四至五個燈柱。未知係咪運作緊。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/j6G8P80.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6G8P80.png&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=031b4a71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/j6G8P80.png</a><br />\n[/img][img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/u21s5Hm.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu21s5Hm.png&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=7e1df81c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/u21s5Hm.png</a><br />\n[/img][img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/c52WY2n.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc52WY2n.png&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=7b170771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/c52WY2n.png</a><br />\n[/img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTNLSno.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTNLSno.png&h=915df166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據立場新聞報道，智慧燈柱試驗計劃為期三年，會在中環和金鐘、銅鑼灣和灣仔、尖沙咀、觀塘和啟德發展區，分階段安裝約 400 支智慧燈柱，其中九龍灣常悅道、啟德承啟道和觀塘市中心，已有 50 支在六月底投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n政府話智慧燈柱只係用作交通情況，氣象等...數據收集，但係呢個港共政府已經係誠信破產，我係唔會信佢。<br />\n基本上，硬件已經存在，要係系統入邊裝什麼監控軟件係好簡單事，同中國買就可以。<br />\n<br />\n如果未來全港九都有呢一種死人燈柱就只能帶面具出街。去邊到，幾點，做過啲乜，都俾人影底，完全冇晒私隱。<br />\n講明啲，真係叫雞都俾比政府知道。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府已經挑戰我哋自由嘅底線，而家再次挑戰我地私穩嘅底線。<br />\n<br />\n根本政府就係想監控我哋。</span><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以幫手救下觀塘人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea30a0c3bb17870ab21806a0665cef81ce404161","tid":1333101,"uid":63392,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"觀塘人留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先可以殲滅呢啲燈柱呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d712f3c6c1079186286712d4eac05d7c6fdc4c","tid":1333101,"uid":283125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ea30a0c3bb17870ab21806a0665cef81ce404161","tid":1333101,"uid":63392,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"觀塘人留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先可以殲滅呢啲燈柱呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:50:04.000Z","msg":"好似無人知觀塘已經出現呢啲燈柱，好似冇人講咁"},{"pid":"bbac212635674827c62434d8ab0c0d2d2090c03c","tid":1333101,"uid":28426,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"九龍灣都好多呀！"},{"pid":"ea162cc995f57ae3e12d3a58f851686a748165f9","tid":1333101,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"油黑個罩"},{"pid":"e0050d944c0b07f7c31c2e97888f5d166115724f","tid":1333101,"uid":269221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:59:17.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"673785952901d71c25d05cc4a6c556aacaac3fcc","tid":1333101,"uid":283125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea162cc995f57ae3e12d3a58f851686a748165f9","tid":1333101,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"油黑個罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"好高喎 大佬"},{"pid":"9745f491d221e0d7f6528a05f78a6965d68d30d0","tid":1333101,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"